# Research Index

The registry and map of every research topic in this project, provided by
`rasa.module.research`. Each topic is a folder under this directory with a
standard structure (`README.md`, `log.md`, `findings.md`, `sources.md`,
`open-questions.md`).

- The rules that govern topics live in **`.claude/research-rules.md`**.
- The per-project seam (research root, tag taxonomy, promotion target) is
  **`.claude/research-canon.md`**.
- `/research` maintains the roster below; `/xref map` refreshes the graph.

This index is a **rollup** — each topic's `README.md` frontmatter is the
source of truth for its status and tags. When they disagree, the frontmatter
wins; re-run `/research` to reconcile.

